    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is it not unusual for a manuscript Amendment to be moved at the last moment like this?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c3a2ea02-1b10-44a3-9121-c3f1689cf299" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
