<p class="">That question does not really arise on the Motion before the Committee.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a40cbcfc-36aa-4108-9d64-8d4ae8d75dc0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
