<p class="">It was a claim which, in the first place, came from the right hon. Gentleman and not from me.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b5731505-a310-4fd0-a77a-ef39cc5a8d6d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
