<p class="">Could we not have the facts?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-f3c6149b-8c74-492e-8d28-9ee715dd5c78" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
