.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stewart, Michael (Fulham, E.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Woodburn, A.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Peto Brig C. H. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stoddart-Scott, Col. M.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Woods, G. S.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pickthorn, K.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stokes, R R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Wyatt, W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Platts-Mills, J. F. F.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Strauss, H. G. (English Universities)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>York, C.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Pools, Cecil (Lichfield)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Stross, Dr. B.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Young, Sir A. S. L. (Partick)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Poole, O. B. S. (Oswestry)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Studholme, H. G.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Younger, Hon. Kenneth</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Popplewell, E.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Summerskill, Dr. Edith</td></p><p class="Division"> <td></td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Porter, E, (Warrington)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Symonds, A. L.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>TELLERS FOR THE AYES:</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Price, M Philips</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Taylor, Vice-Adm. E. A, (P'dd't'n, S.)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Mr. Hannan and Mr. Wilkins.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division"> </table></p><p class="Division"> <table type="span"></p><p class="